       We may update our privacy policy from time to time.  
       We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page.  
   </p>  
   <br>  
   <h2 class="text-dark">Contact Us</h2>  
   <p>  
       If you have any questions about our privacy policy, please contact us at the email address:  
       <a href="mailto:privacy@bookcase.com" class="text-decoration-none">privacy@bookcase.com</a>  
